00065     void ResourceManager::ApplyShapeToActor(ActorBase* Actor, btCollisionShape* ColShape)
00066     {
00067         if(ActorBase::Actorrigid == Actor->GetType())
00068         {
00069             btRigidBody* Rigid = static_cast < btRigidBody* > (Actor->CollisionObject);
00070             btScalar mass = Rigid->getInvMass();
00071             mass=1/mass;
00072             btVector3 inertia(0,0,0);
00073             ColShape->calculateLocalInertia(mass, inertia);
00074             Rigid->setMassProps(mass,inertia);
00075         }
00076         if(ActorBase::Actorragdoll == Actor->GetType())
00077         {
00078         }
00079         if(!Actor->ShapeIsSaved)
00080         {
00081             delete Actor->Shape;
00082         }
00083         Actor->CollisionObject->setCollisionShape(ColShape);
00084         Actor->Shape = ColShape;
00085     }

00087     bool ResourceManager::ExportShapeData(ActorBase* Actor, String &FileName)
00088     {
00089         btDefaultSerializer* Serializer = new btDefaultSerializer(1024*1024*5);
00090         Serializer->startSerialization();
00091         int len = Actor->Shape->calculateSerializeBufferSize();
00092         btChunk* chunk = Serializer->allocate(len,1);
00093         const char* structType = Actor->Shape->serialize(chunk->m_oldPtr, Serializer);
00094         Serializer->finalizeChunk(chunk,structType,BT_SHAPE_CODE,Actor->Shape);
00095         Serializer->finishSerialization();
00096         FILE* f2 = fopen(FileName.c_str(),"wb");
00097         size_t verify = fwrite(Serializer->getBufferPointer(),Serializer->getCurrentBufferSize(),1,f2);
00098         fclose(f2);
00099         if(1 != verify)
00100         {
00101             return false;
00102         }
00103         return true;
00104     }

00106     bool ResourceManager::ImportShapeData(ActorBase* Actor, String &FileName)
00107     {
00108         btBulletWorldImporter* Importer = new btBulletWorldImporter();
00109 
00110         //Check root directory first
00111         if(Importer->loadFile(FileName.c_str()))
00112         {
00113             btCollisionShape* shape = Importer->getCollisionShapeByIndex(0);
00114             if(shape)
00115             {
00116                 ApplyShapeToActor(Actor, shape);
00117                 delete Importer;
00118                 return true;
00119             }
00120             delete Importer;
00121             return false;
00122         }
00123 
00124         Ogre::DataStreamPtr Stream = OgreResource->openResource(FileName);
00125         char* buffer = new char[Stream->size()];
00126         Stream->read((void*)buffer, Stream->size());
00127         if(Importer->loadFileFromMemory(buffer, Stream->size()))
00128         {
00129             btCollisionShape* shape = Importer->getCollisionShapeByIndex(0);
00130             if(shape)
00131             {
00132                 ApplyShapeToActor(Actor, shape);
00133                 delete buffer;
00134                 delete Importer;
00135                 return true;
00136             }
00137             delete buffer;
00138             delete Importer;
00139             return false;
00140         }
00141 
00142         delete buffer;
00143         delete Importer;
00144         return false;
00145     }
